分<br />\n人生仲有好多野煩<br />\n所以比自己低落一陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76fe158154061a5ceab78b5979ce66e77346af36","tid":105131,"uid":57990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T17:05:50.000Z","msg":"邊方面失意啊"},{"pid":"da68d0ee8afedd37eb78bdf2c88ed54899185f8d","tid":105131,"uid":53272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T17:06:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我好鐘意你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你講我ac名定咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adf00b085bc61e3fc5ec695363d269283fdd0888","tid":105131,"uid":53272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T17:07:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊方面失意啊</blockquote><br />\n好多野做好又好似無做好<br />\n想做又無能力做到<br />\n只係覺得人生好多野煩惱<br />\n比自己情緒發洩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c005f74e360aecfb81a0863cb1d1181291f05375","tid":105131,"uid":53272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T17:08:31.000Z","msg":"明明已經溫柔左<br />\n努力左 表達左<br />\n但好似徒勞無功"},{"pid":"323d2970c0718965ec17f32436db42d7fb4851b0","tid":105131,"uid":24904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T17:09:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我好鐘意你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你講我ac名定咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望你能夠好似你個名咁 看透世事<br />\n減少啲煩惱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a54d95d79e409031c00e4fd74a90c5cc1ed9b79f","tid":105131,"uid":53272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T17:09:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>明明已經溫柔左<br />\n努力左 表達左<br />\n但好似徒勞無功</blockquote><br />\n其實改善左 改變左<br />\n你有冇察覺到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"